'''卡拉蒙战役'''（英文：'''Battle of Qalamoun'''）是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中的一次战役。该战役开始于2013年11月15日敘利亞政府军对位于[[卡拉蒙|卡拉蒙]]卡拉镇（Qara）的空袭行动。这场战役的目的是政府军试图切断反对派的[[大马士革|大马士革]]与[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]之间的[[补给线|补给线]]。<ref name="fierce">{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/fierce-syria-clashes-spark-exodus-lebanon-2013111712321697322.html |title=Fierce Syria clashes spark exodus to Lebanon |publisher=Al Jazeera |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2019-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517231741/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2013/11/fierce-syria-clashes-spark-exodus-lebanon-2013111712321697322.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>这一重要地区已经被反对派武装用作发动针对大马士革周边地区行动的重要后方基地。而政府军方面需要该地区附近的[[高速公路|高速公路]]连接大马士革和[[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]中部地区，并且在该地区有很多武器仓库。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-lebanon-monitor.aspx?pageID=238&nID=58038&NewsCatID=352 |title=Syria air force bombards town near Lebanon: monitor |work=Hürriyet Daily News |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019071844/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-lebanon-monitor.aspx?pageID=238&nID=58038&NewsCatID=352 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==攻占卡拉镇==
在11月15日至17日间，在政府军发出警告表示将进攻该地区的反对派武装之后，1200－1700个家庭（约占卡拉镇90%）逃离该镇前往黎巴嫩小镇Arsal<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2013/Nov-16/238049-syrian-families-cross-into-lebanon-from-qalamoun.ashx#axzz2kuran5Dc |title=Thousands of Syrians from Qalamoun flee to Lebanon |work=The Daily Star |location=Lebanon |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111220905/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2013/Nov-16/238049-syrian-families-cross-into-lebanon-from-qalamoun.ashx#axzz2kuran5Dc |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Blast near Damascus kills 31 troops: monitor |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Nov-17/238118-31-troops-killed-in-blast-near-damascus-activists.ashx#axzz2k3r8IiK5 |work=The Daily Star |date=17 November 2013 |accessdate=17 November 2013 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211040626/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Nov-17/238118-31-troops-killed-in-blast-near-damascus-activists.ashx#axzz2k3r8IiK5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。作为这场进攻的准备，数以千计的黎巴嫩真主党武装分子前往卡拉蒙地区边境对面的黎巴嫩一侧并驻扎下来。<ref name="launches"/>

11月15日，政府军发动了一场针对该地区的攻势，<ref>{{cite web |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.mininggazette.com/page/content.detail/id/409877/Syrian-army-launches-offensive-near-Lebanon-border.html?isap=1&nav=5016 |title=Syrian army launches offensive near Lebanon border |publisher=Mininggazette.com |date=16 November 2013 |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2013-11-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131118023323/http://www.mininggazette.com/page/content.detail/id/409877/Syrian-army-launches-offensive-near-Lebanon-border.html?isap=1&nav=5016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>并且第二天多次空袭了反对派控制的该镇。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/86676/World/Region/Syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-Lebanon.aspx |title=Syria air force bombards town near Lebanon |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926193601/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/86676/World/Region/Syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-Lebanon.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>战斗也在奈卜克镇和Rima镇附近展开。<ref>{{cite web |author=Ryan Lucas, Associated Press |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/news/nation_world/20131117_Assad_gaining_ground_in_Syrian_civil_war.html |title=Assad gaining ground in Syrian civil war |work=Philadelphia Daily News |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2013-11-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131118023159/http://www.philly.com/philly/news/nation_world/20131117_Assad_gaining_ground_in_Syrian_civil_war.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |agency=Reuters |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-syrian-army-fights-for-road-needed-to-remove-chemical-weapons/1791527.html |title=Syrian Army Fights for Road Needed to Remove Chemical Weapons |publisher=Voice of America |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928163624/http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-syrian-army-fights-for-road-needed-to-remove-chemical-weapons/1791527.html |archive-date=2015-09-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> <ref name="launches">{{cite web |url=http://www.thonline.com/news/national_world/article_831c0a3c-c749-5de1-bd53-138e8c590ece.html |title=Syrian army launches offensive near Lebanon border |publisher=Thonline.com |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128073703/http://www.thonline.com/news/national_world/article_831c0a3c-c749-5de1-bd53-138e8c590ece.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>该地区的反对派武装被动员起来抵抗政府军的进攻。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian army fights for road needed to remove chemical weapons |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/16/us-syria-crisis-road-idUSBRE9AF06920131116?feedType=RSS&dlvrit=992637 |agency=Reuters |date=16 November 2013 |accessdate=16 November 2013 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929004514/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/16/us-syria-crisis-road-idUSBRE9AF06920131116?feedType=RSS&dlvrit=992637 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

11月17日，政府军向卡拉镇周边的山区推进，<ref>{{cite web |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/world/syrias-qalamoun-offensive-forces-thousands-to-flee-to-lebanon/article5361017.ece |title=Syria's Qalamoun offensive forces thousands to flee to Lebanon |work=The Hindu |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128073504/http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/world/syrias-qalamoun-offensive-forces-thousands-to-flee-to-lebanon/article5361017.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>并试图进攻该镇，<ref name="fierce"/>使该镇遭遇了更多的空袭和炮击。<ref>{{cite web |author=Liz Sly |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/syria-fighting-in-qalamoun-triggers-new-exodus-of-refugees-to-lebanon/2013/11/17/f08641cc-4fb4-11e3-9ee6-2580086d8254_story.html |title=Syria fighting in Qalamoun triggers new exodus of refugees to Lebanon |work=The Washington Post |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022134328/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/syria-fighting-in-qalamoun-triggers-new-exodus-of-refugees-to-lebanon/2013/11/17/f08641cc-4fb4-11e3-9ee6-2580086d8254_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/thomson-reuters/131117/syrian-army-besieges-town-strategic-qalamoun-mountains |title=Syrian army besieges town in strategic Qalamoun mountains |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029054917/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/thomson-reuters/131117/syrian-army-besieges-town-strategic-qalamoun-mountains |dead-url=no }}</ref>直至当天下午，政府军仍未能攻入该镇。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://byonlineweb.com/2013/11/17/syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-lebanon-monitor/ |title=Syria air force bombards town near Lebanon: monitor |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021123214/http://byonlineweb.com/2013/11/17/syria-air-force-bombards-town-near-lebanon-monitor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

冲突使得大马士革和霍姆斯之间的高速公路中断通车。

11月18日，政府军继续攻势。根据亲政府的al-Watan日报报道，政府军攻占了卡拉镇的关键地区。<ref>{{cite news |title=Syrian troops recapture key positions in northern Damascus' town |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-11/18/c_132897876.htm |agency=Xinhua News Agency |date=18 November 2013 |accessdate=18 November 2013 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128055939/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2013-11/18/c_132897876.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>叙利亚空军还多次空袭了盖莱蒙山区和耶卜鲁德山区。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://documents.sy/news.php?id=9294&lang=en |title=Damascus Countryside |accessdate=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025144037/http://documents.sy/news.php?id=9294&lang=en |dead-url=yes }}</ref>一名逃往黎巴嫩的当地居民描述了对卡拉镇的攻击“卡拉镇完了”。<ref>{{cite web |last=Yacoub |first=Khaled |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/18/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE9AH0NU20131118 |title=Syria rebel chieftain killed; Assad forces bomb besieged town |agency=Reuters |access-date=2014-02-16 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190942/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/11/18/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE9AH0NU20131118 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

